<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Book Shelf</title>

        <style>
            html {
                background-color: whitesmoke;
            }
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                background-color: white;
                width: 50rem;
                margin: 3rem auto;
                max-width: 90%;
                padding: 2rem;
                box-shadow: 0 .05rem .5rem #e5e5e5;
            }
            h1 {
                margin: 1rem .75rem;
            }
            /* ul {
                list-style: none;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                display: flex;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
            }
            li {
                margin: 10px;
                padding: 10px;
                background-color: #f2f2f2;
                border-radius: 5px;
                box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
                text-align: center;
                width: 200px;
            } */
            li{
                margin: .5rem 0;
            }
            a {
                text-decoration: none;
                color: #333;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>你的书架 清单</h1>
        <% if (locals.books.length) { %>
            <ul>
                <% locals.books.forEach(book => { %>
                    <li> <a href="download?name=<%= encodeURIComponent(book) %>"><%= book %></a></li>
                <% }); %>
            </ul>
        <% } else { %>
            <br>
            <hr>
            <br>
            <p>你还没有添加任何书籍到你的书架。</p>
            <p>或者是没有选择“epub模式”转换成epub?</p>
        <% } %>
    </body>
</html>